{"tid":707290,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"7歲仔好鐘意玩啫啫，點教好？","createTime":"2018-06-18T14:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T15:53:31.000Z","uid":49974,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f8140e3c3f0a42ab24f09037b6e09959c85a8fb4","tid":707290,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:12:18.000Z","msg":"打又打過，鬧又鬧過<br />\n好聲好氣咁教佢又係咁<br />\n親我訓左教就自己係到攪<br />\n岩岩朝早又係咁，同我訓訓下<br />\n自己走左出去，我覺得奇怪<br />\n就跟出去睇下佢做乜，點知佢又反自己間房係到攪啫，激到我死<br />\n嬲到我話用鉸剪剪左佢算啦喊<br />\n佢就係到大喊大叫，最後我冇佢辦法叫佢行埋一邊舉手罰企<br />\n有冇人可以教竹下我點教好呀，<br />\n真係俾呢個仔激死架啦！"},{"pid":"726fb23440904ed75de6eb3df97fcb78822998da","tid":707290,"uid":86756,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:13:38.000Z","msg":"🥖😍"},{"pid":"de36b835edd2315241a6b8d56e8e654f650dfce1","tid":707290,"uid":113178,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:15:02.000Z","msg":"7歲囡囡就話唔太好姐，仔仔就由佢啦遲早日日玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d74f5c8c0e769f6dacbab385d1126ff7a5cbe7","tid":707290,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:15:17.000Z","msg":"都真係天生淫蕩"},{"pid":"e4d95ac0275c7965e1adec925537188f1bdb054b","tid":707290,"uid":165213,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:16:57.000Z","msg":"咁細個打j 會變蠢 一定要阻止"},{"pid":"afa0e54a23ef90d2cc6baebefdce946236b0f377","tid":707290,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:17:14.000Z","msg":"幫下佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68fae860d138c48ec930463eb3c0c03a3c06aa3e","tid":707290,"uid":173342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:18:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c33e5db1cfb430ef1aa145aeef0e2996838c396d","tid":707290,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:19:07.000Z","